Package cz.cuni.mff.kocur.agent

Package that implements the agent and all the necessary classes, that let the user control it.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AgentController
    This interface represents a controller.
    BotFunction<O,T>
    Interface that represents a parametrized function with calculate method().
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AgentContext
    Represents a bot's contextual information.
    AgentLoader
    The purpose of this class is to load agents from framework configuration.
    AgentParameters
    AgentParameters for entities.
    BaseAgentController
    Abstract class that implements some of the methods that can be used by sample Controller.
    BuySequence
    This class represents a buy sequence.
    Context
    Abstract class that represents a context.
    ControllersManager
    This class manages all the controllers.
    ControllerWrapper
    Wraps around the Agent's Controller to create some more functionality and control.
    EntityParameter
    Parameter that can be extended and that is used to stored some parameters, that can be useful to entities.
    InterestParameter
    Parameter that can be extended and that is used to stored some parameters, that can be useful to interest objects.
    LevelUpSequence
    Class that stores ability indexes, that a agent wants to take.
    Roles
    Class with all the roles a player can play.
    SelectedAgentDummy
    Simple class that server to deserialize botsselected body that is passed by the game.
    TeamContext
    Class that represents team's context.
